column6: Are there any changes you would like to see to the Meal Exchange website?
haven't really used it before because i don't even know how to, so i'm excited to see how this turns out!
I wish the site would directly share information with clubs, rather than having eating clubs make students fill out secondary forms/sheets, which are super annoying at Cap and TI.
I forget if this is already there so I apologize if so but I wish there was a way to cancel a meal swap. Sometimes I set it up but don’t end up eating there.
Whenever I’ve done meal exchange the upperclassman has always done it so I really have no idea what the website is like.
Didn't really use it that much
